Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Under my leadership, America will once again stand shoulder to shoulder with our friend and ally, the state of Israel... I will always defend Israel’s fundamental right to EXIST as a Jewish nation in the Jewish homeland...If Kamala Harris wins, instead of the most pro-Israel president ever... you will have the most ANTI-Israel president by far."
